 are able to achieve comparable\nperformance to contemporary approaches at a fraction of the overall model\ncomplexity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Dec 2020 20:38:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-11"}
