s. Our model provides insight into how\ncontraction propagation affects flow rates and transport through a lymphangion\nchain.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Dec 2020 00:12:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 4 Jul 2021 22:05:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-06"}
