acy as well as energy dissipation of the proposed ES-PFEM.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Dec 2020 11:54:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 11 Dec 2020 03:36:17 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 20 Aug 2021 08:42:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-26"}
