 that, for the specific application domain considered here, our\nproposed solution shows good convergence performance and superior runtime\ncompared to HMC.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Dec 2020 15:26:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 14 Dec 2020 16:19:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-15"}
