data and the testing data, 3) it has achieved 96\\%\nclassification accuracy, which is 13\\% higher classification accuracy than\n\"non-transfer\" algorithms, and 8\\% higher than existing transfer and distant\ntransfer algorithms.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Dec 2020 02:53:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-14"}
